{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841873325,"sessionID":"ses_28793b96fffeRkvD3Rh6IUMx22","part":{"id":"prt_d786c80e0001XebcXzQ7QflXt3","messageID":"msg_d786c72a9001uIWq4y2HGTXkLb","sessionID":"ses_28793b96fffeRkvD3Rh6IUMx22","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-4b8d90a47a13467f84f6b4ce42f789be","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | M |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，提供 RESTful API 基础设施、中间件架构、生命周期管理。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: ```\n20: cmd/workload-manager/\n21:     └── main.go                    — 入口，调用 pkg/workloadmanager\n22: pkg/workloadmanager/\n23:     ├── server.go                  — HTTPServer 核心实现\n24:     ├── router.go                  — 路由配置与路由组\n25:     ├── config.go                  — 配置结构体\n26:     ├── types.go                   — 公共类型定义\n27:     ├── handlers/\n28:     │   ├── handler.go             — Handler 接口\n29:     │   └── health.go              — 健康检查实现\n30:     └── middleware/\n31:         ├── logging.go             — 请求日志中间件\n32:         ├── recovery.go            — Panic 恢复中间件\n33:         └── cors.go                — CORS 中间件\n34: ```\n35: \n36: ### Dependencies\n37: \n38: | Package | Purpose |\n39: |---------|---------|\n40: | `net/http` | 标准库 HTTP 服务器 |\n41: | `context` | 请求上下文 |\n42: | `sync` | 并发控制（优雅关闭） |\n43: | `os/signal` | 信号处理 |\n44: | `time` | 超时配置 |\n45: \n46: ### Router Library Selection\n47: \n48: **决策**: 使用 `go-chi/chi` v5\n49: \n50: | Aspect | Rationale |\n51: |--------|-----------|\n52: | 零外部依赖 | 仅依赖 Go 标准库 |\n53: | 兼容 net/http | 可使用所有标准库中间件 |\n54: | 路由分组 | 支持路由组与中间件作用域 |\n55: | 性能 | 足够优秀（参考 benchmark） |\n56: \n57: ## Data Structures\n58: \n59: ### server.go\n60: \n61: ```go\n62: type HTTPServer struct {\n63:     server   *http.Server\n64:     router   chi.Router\n65:     config   Config\n66:     handlers map[string]Handler\n67:     logger   Logger\n68:     stopCh   chan struct{}\n69: }\n70: \n71: type Config struct {\n72:     Addr              string        // 监听地址，如 \":8080\"\n73:     ReadTimeout       time.Duration // 读超时\n74:     WriteTimeout      time.Duration // 写超时\n75:     IdleTimeout       time.Duration // 空闲连接超时\n76:     ShutdownTimeout   time.Duration // 优雅关闭超时\n77:     EnableHealthz     bool          // 是否启用健康检查\n78:     EnableReadyz      bool          // 是否启用就绪探针\n79: }\n80: ```\n81: \n82: ### router.go\n83: \n84: ```go\n85: type Router struct {\n86:     chi.Router\n87: }\n88: \n89: func NewRouter() *Router {\n90:     r := chi.NewRouter()\n91:     return &Router{Router: r}\n92: }\n93: \n94: func (r *Router) RegisterHandlers(handlers ...Handler) {\n95:     for _, h := range handlers {\n96:         h.Register(r.Router)\n97:     }\n98: }\n99: ```\n100: \n101: ### handlers/handler.go\n102: \n103: ```go\n104: type Handler interface {\n105:     Register(r chi.Router)\n106: }\n107: \n108: type HandlerFunc func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) error\n109: \n110: func (hf HandlerFunc) ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n111:     if err := hf(w, r); err != nil {\n112:         HandleError(w, r, err)\n113:     }\n114: }\n115: ```\n116: \n117: ### handlers/health.go\n118: \n119: ```go\n120: type HealthHandler struct {\n121:     checker HealthChecker\n122: }\n123: \n124: type HealthChecker interface {\n125:     IsHealthy() bool\n126:     IsReady() bool\n127: }\n128: \n129: func (h *HealthHandler) Register(r chi.Router) {\n130:     r.Get(\"/healthz\", h.healthz)\n131:     r.Get(\"/readyz\", h.readyz)\n132: }\n133: \n134: func (h *HealthHandler) healthz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n135:     w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n136:     json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"ok\"})\n137: }\n138: \n139: func (h *HealthHandler) readyz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n140:     if h.checker == nil || !h.checker.IsReady() {\n141:         w.WriteHeader(http.StatusServiceUnavailable)\n142:         json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"not ready\"})\n143:         return\n144:     }\n145:     w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n146:     json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"ready\"})\n147: }\n148: ```\n149: \n150: ### middleware/logging.go\n151: \n152: ```go\n153: type LoggingMiddleware struct {\n154:     logger Logger\n155: }\n156: \n157: func (m *LoggingMiddleware) Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n158:     return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n159:         start := time.Now()\n160:         \n161:         ww := &responseWriterWrapper{ResponseWriter: w}\n162:         next.ServeHTTP(ww, r)\n163:         \n164:         m.logger.Info(\"request\",\n165:             \"method\", r.Method,\n166:             \"path\", r.URL.Path,\n167:             \"status\", ww.status,\n168:             \"duration\", time.Since(start),\n169:         )\n170:     })\n171: }\n172: ```\n173: \n174: ### middleware/recovery.go\n175: \n176: ```go\n177: type RecoveryMiddleware struct {\n178:     logger Logger\n179: }\n180: \n181: func (m *RecoveryMiddleware) Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n182:     return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n183:         defer func() {\n184:             if err := recover(); err != nil {\n185:                 m.logger.Error(\"panic recovered\", \"error\", err, \"path\", r.URL.Path)\n186:                 http.Error(w, \"Internal Server Error\", http.StatusInternalServerError)\n187:             }\n188:         }()\n189:         next.ServeHTTP(w, r)\n190:     })\n191: }\n192: ```\n193: \n194: ### types.go\n195: \n196: ```go\n197: type ErrorResponse struct {\n198:     Code    string `json:\"code\"`\n199:     Message string `json:\"message\"`\n200:     Details any    `json:\"details,omitempty\"`\n201: }\n202: \n203: type SuccessResponse struct {\n204:     Data any `json:\"data\"`\n205: }\n206: \n207: func HandleError(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request, err error) {\n208:     // 根据 error 类型映射到 HTTP 状态码\n209:     // 统一返回 ErrorResponse JSON\n210: }\n211: ```\n212: \n213: ## API Endpoints\n214: \n215: ### Health Endpoints\n216: \n217: | Endpoint | Method | Purpose |\n218: |----------|--------|---------|\n219: | `/healthz` | GET | 健康检查（Kubernetes liveness probe） |\n220: | `/readyz` | GET | 就绪探针（Kubernetes readiness probe） |\n221: \n222: ### API Group\n223: \n224: | Prefix | Purpose |\n225: |--------|---------|\n226: | `/api/v1` | 业务 API 路由组（待后续 AR 实现） |\n227: \n228: ### Middleware Chain\n229: \n230: ```\n231: Recovery → Logging → CORS (optional) → Business Handler\n232: ```\n233: \n234: ## Error Handling\n235: \n236: | Error Type | HTTP Status | Error Code |\n237: |------------|-------------|------------|\n238: | Validation Error | 400 | `VALIDATION_ERROR` |\n239: | Not Found | 404 | `NOT_FOUND` |\n240: | Internal Error | 500 | `INTERNAL_ERROR` |\n241: | Service Unavailable | 503 | `SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE` |\n242: \n243: 统一错误响应格式:\n244: ```json\n245: {\n246:   \"code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n247:   \"message\": \"Invalid request parameter\",\n248:   \"details\": {\"field\": \"name\", \"reason\": \"required\"}\n249: }\n250: ```\n251: \n252: ## Testing Strategy\n253: \n254: ### Unit Tests\n255: \n256: | Test Category | Coverage |\n257: |---------------|----------|\n258: | HTTPServer 启动/关闭 | 测试优雅关闭逻辑 |\n259: | HealthHandler | 测试 `/healthz` 和 `/readyz` 端点 |\n260: | Middleware | 测试日志、恢复、CORS 中间件 |\n261: | 错误处理 | 测试 HandleError 返回正确的 JSON 格式 |\n262: \n263: ### Integration Tests\n264: \n265: | Test | Description |\n266: |------|-------------|\n267: | 端到端请求 | 启动真实 HTTP 服务器，发送请求并验证响应 |\n268: | 中间件链 | 验证中间件按预期顺序执行 |\n269: \n270: ### Test File Structure\n271: \n272: ```\n273: pkg/workloadmanager/\n274:   server_test.go\n275:   router_test.go\n276:   handlers/health_test.go\n277:   middleware/logging_test.go\n278:   middleware/recovery_test.go\n279: ```\n280: \n281: ## File Structure\n282: \n283: ```\n284: pkg/workloadmanager/\n285:   server.go              — HTTPServer 实现\n286:   router.go              — Router 封装\n287:   config.go              — Config 结构体\n288:   types.go               — 公共类型定义\n289:   handlers/\n290:     handler.go           — Handler 接口\n291:     health.go            — HealthHandler 实现\n292:   middleware/\n293:     logging.go           — 日志中间件\n294:     recovery.go          — Panic 恢复中间件\n295:     cors.go              — CORS 中间件\n296: ```\n297: \n298: ## Open Questions\n299: \n300: - 是否需要 WebSocket 支持？（暂不在范围内，待后续 AR）\n301: - 是否需要限流中间件？（暂不在范围内，待后续 AR）\n302: - 日志库选型：pkg/logging 还是第三方（如 zap、logrus）？\n303: - 指标端点 `/metrics` 是否在本 AR 范围内？（建议预留路由，实现待后续 AR）\n304: \n305: ## References\n306: \n307: - chi router: https://github.com/go-chi/chi\n308: - Go net/http: https://pkg.go.dev/net/http\n309: - Kubernetes API conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n\n(End of file - total 309 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，提供 RESTful API 基础设施、中间件架构、生命周期管理。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\ncmd/workload-manager/","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","time":{"start":1775841873302,"end":1775841873323}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841873329,"sessionID":"ses_28793b96fffeRkvD3Rh6IUMx22","part":{"id":"prt_d786c85240017swbjoH4n2Wy32","messageID":"msg_d786c72a9001uIWq4y2HGTXkLb","sessionID":"ses_28793b96fffeRkvD3Rh6IUMx22","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-4e3730c40083409fb7c08cc8084400fc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package v1alpha1\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \tcorev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"\n5: \tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n6: )\n7: \n8: // AgentRuntime is the Schema for the agentruntimes API.\n9: // It represents a runtime configuration for an AI agent sandbox,\n10: // including pod templates, session timeouts, and network port configurations.\n11: //\n12: // +genclient\n13: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n14: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n15: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n16: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n17: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n18: type AgentRuntime struct {\n19: \tmetav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n20: \tmetav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n21: \n22: \tSpec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n23: \tStatus AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n24: }\n25: \n26: // AgentRuntimeSpec defines the desired state of AgentRuntime.\n27: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n28: \t// Ports specifies the network ports to expose from the sandbox.\n29: \t// +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n30: \t// +listType=atomic\n31: \tPorts []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n32: \n33: \t// Template defines the pod template for the sandbox.\n34: \t// +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n35: \tTemplate *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n36: \n37: \t// SessionTimeout specifies the idle timeout for a session.\n38: \t// Default is 15 minutes.\n39: \t// +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n40: \t// +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n41: \tSessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n42: \n43: \t// MaxSessionDuration specifies the maximum duration a session can exist.\n44: \t// Default is 8 hours.\n45: \t// +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n46: \t// +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n47: \tMaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n48: }\n49: \n50: // AgentRuntimeStatus defines the observed state of AgentRuntime.\n51: type AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n52: \t// Conditions represents the latest available observations of the AgentRuntime's state.\n53: \t// +optional\n54: \t// +listType=atomic\n55: \tConditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n56: }\n57: \n58: // SandboxTemplate defines the pod template for creating sandbox pods.\n59: type SandboxTemplate struct {\n60: \t// Labels are applied to the sandbox pod.\n61: \t// +optional\n62: \tLabels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,rep,name=labels\"`\n63: \n64: \t// Annotations are applied to the sandbox pod.\n65: \t// +optional\n66: \tAnnotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,rep,name=annotations\"`\n67: \n68: \t// Spec is the PodSpec for the sandbox pod.\n69: \t// +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n70: \tSpec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=spec\"`\n71: }\n72: \n73: // AgentRuntimeList contains a list of AgentRuntime resources.\n74: //\n75: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n76: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n77: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n78: \tmetav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n79: \tmetav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n80: \n81: \tItems []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n82: }\n\n(End of file - total 82 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package v1alpha1\n\nimport (\n\tcorev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"\n\tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n)\n\n// AgentRuntime is the Schema for the agentruntimes API.\n// It represents a runtime configuration for an AI agent sandbox,\n// including pod templates, session timeouts, and network port configurations.\n//\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n\tmetav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n\tmetav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go","time":{"start":1775841873306,"end":1775841873328}}}}
