{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841923316,"sessionID":"ses_28793b96fffeRkvD3Rh6IUMx22","part":{"id":"prt_d786d50be001Yg87Ao3EB4woo7","messageID":"msg_d786cddc3001loquPPGtxWq3h7","sessionID":"ses_28793b96fffeRkvD3Rh6IUMx22","type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"toolu_tool-c7f409f9103c42d0a76bf845756be162","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","oldString":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，提供 RESTful API 基础设施、中间件架构、生命周期管理。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\ncmd/workload-manager/\n    └── main.go                    — 入口，调用 pkg/workloadmanager\npkg/workloadmanager/\n    ├── server.go                  — HTTPServer 核心实现\n    ├── router.go                  — 路由配置与路由组\n    ├── config.go                  — 配置结构体\n    ├── types.go                   — 公共类型定义\n    ├── handlers/\n    │   ├── handler.go             — Handler 接口\n    │   └── health.go              — 健康检查实现\n    └── middleware/\n        ├── logging.go             — 请求日志中间件\n        ├── recovery.go            — Panic 恢复中间件\n        └── cors.go                — CORS 中间件\n```","newString":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，提供 RESTful API 基础设施、中间件架构、生命周期管理。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\ncmd/workload-manager/\n    └── main.go                    — 入口，调用 pkg/workloadmanager\npkg/workloadmanager/\n    ├── server.go                  — HTTPServer 核心实现\n    ├── router.go                  — 路由配置与路由组\n    ├── config.go                  — 配置结构体\n    ├── types.go                   — 公共类型定义\n    ├── doc.go                     — 包文档\n    ├── handlers/\n    │   ├── handler.go             — Handler 接口\n    │   └── health.go              — 健康检查实现\n    └── middleware/\n        ├── logging.go             — 请求日志中间件\n        ├── recovery.go            — Panic 恢复中间件\n        └── cors.go                — CORS 中间件\n```\n\n### Kubernetes Client Integration\n\nWorkloadManager 使用 `client-go` 与 Kubernetes API 交互:\n\n| Client | API Group | Resource | Purpose |\n|--------|-----------|----------|---------|\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` | `agentruntimes` | 管理 AgentRuntime CR |\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` | `codeinterpreters` | 管理 CodeInterpreter CR |\n\nClient construction pattern:\n\n```go\nimport (\n    versioned \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n    \"k8s.io/client-go/rest\"\n)\n\nfunc NewKubernetesClient(config *rest.Config) (versioned.Interface, error) {\n    return versioned.NewForConfig(config)\n}\n```\n\nTyped client interfaces:\n\n```go\ntype RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n    RESTClient() rest.Interface\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n    CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterInterface\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n}\n```"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go":[]},"diff":"Index: /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md\n===================================================================\n--- /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md\n+++ /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md\n@@ -23,8 +23,9 @@\n     ├── server.go                  — HTTPServer 核心实现\n     ├── router.go                  — 路由配置与路由组\n     ├── config.go                  — 配置结构体\n     ├── types.go                   — 公共类型定义\n+    ├── doc.go                     — 包文档\n     ├── handlers/\n     │   ├── handler.go             — Handler 接口\n     │   └── health.go              — 健康检查实现\n     └── middleware/\n@@ -32,8 +33,51 @@\n         ├── recovery.go            — Panic 恢复中间件\n         └── cors.go                — CORS 中间件\n ```\n \n+### Kubernetes Client Integration\n+\n+WorkloadManager 使用 `client-go` 与 Kubernetes API 交互:\n+\n+| Client | API Group | Resource | Purpose |\n+|--------|-----------|----------|---------|\n+| `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` | `agentruntimes` | 管理 AgentRuntime CR |\n+| `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` | `codeinterpreters` | 管理 CodeInterpreter CR |\n+\n+Client construction pattern:\n+\n+```go\n+import (\n+    versioned \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n+    \"k8s.io/client-go/rest\"\n+)\n+\n+func NewKubernetesClient(config *rest.Config) (versioned.Interface, error) {\n+    return versioned.NewForConfig(config)\n+}\n+```\n+\n+Typed client interfaces:\n+\n+```go\n+type RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n+    RESTClient() rest.Interface\n+    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n+    CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterInterface\n+}\n+\n+type AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n+    Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n+    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n+    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n+    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n+    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n+    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n+    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n+    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n+}\n+```\n+\n ### Dependencies\n \n | Package | Purpose |\n |---------|---------|\n","filediff":{"file":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","before":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，提供 RESTful API 基础设施、中间件架构、生命周期管理。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\ncmd/workload-manager/\n    └── main.go                    — 入口，调用 pkg/workloadmanager\npkg/workloadmanager/\n    ├── server.go                  — HTTPServer 核心实现\n    ├── router.go                  — 路由配置与路由组\n    ├── config.go                  — 配置结构体\n    ├── types.go                   — 公共类型定义\n    ├── handlers/\n    │   ├── handler.go             — Handler 接口\n    │   └── health.go              — 健康检查实现\n    └── middleware/\n        ├── logging.go             — 请求日志中间件\n        ├── recovery.go            — Panic 恢复中间件\n        └── cors.go                — CORS 中间件\n```\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `net/http` | 标准库 HTTP 服务器 |\n| `context` | 请求上下文 |\n| `sync` | 并发控制（优雅关闭） |\n| `os/signal` | 信号处理 |\n| `time` | 超时配置 |\n\n### Router Library Selection\n\n**决策**: 使用 `go-chi/chi` v5\n\n| Aspect | Rationale |\n|--------|-----------|\n| 零外部依赖 | 仅依赖 Go 标准库 |\n| 兼容 net/http | 可使用所有标准库中间件 |\n| 路由分组 | 支持路由组与中间件作用域 |\n| 性能 | 足够优秀（参考 benchmark） |\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### server.go\n\n```go\ntype HTTPServer struct {\n    server   *http.Server\n    router   chi.Router\n    config   Config\n    handlers map[string]Handler\n    logger   Logger\n    stopCh   chan struct{}\n}\n\ntype Config struct {\n    Addr              string        // 监听地址，如 \":8080\"\n    ReadTimeout       time.Duration // 读超时\n    WriteTimeout      time.Duration // 写超时\n    IdleTimeout       time.Duration // 空闲连接超时\n    ShutdownTimeout   time.Duration // 优雅关闭超时\n    EnableHealthz     bool          // 是否启用健康检查\n    EnableReadyz      bool          // 是否启用就绪探针\n}\n```\n\n### router.go\n\n```go\ntype Router struct {\n    chi.Router\n}\n\nfunc NewRouter() *Router {\n    r := chi.NewRouter()\n    return &Router{Router: r}\n}\n\nfunc (r *Router) RegisterHandlers(handlers ...Handler) {\n    for _, h := range handlers {\n        h.Register(r.Router)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### handlers/handler.go\n\n```go\ntype Handler interface {\n    Register(r chi.Router)\n}\n\ntype HandlerFunc func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) error\n\nfunc (hf HandlerFunc) ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n    if err := hf(w, r); err != nil {\n        HandleError(w, r, err)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### handlers/health.go\n\n```go\ntype HealthHandler struct {\n    checker HealthChecker\n}\n\ntype HealthChecker interface {\n    IsHealthy() bool\n    IsReady() bool\n}\n\nfunc (h *HealthHandler) Register(r chi.Router) {\n    r.Get(\"/healthz\", h.healthz)\n    r.Get(\"/readyz\", h.readyz)\n}\n\nfunc (h *HealthHandler) healthz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n    w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n    json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"ok\"})\n}\n\nfunc (h *HealthHandler) readyz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n    if h.checker == nil || !h.checker.IsReady() {\n        w.WriteHeader(http.StatusServiceUnavailable)\n        json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"not ready\"})\n        return\n    }\n    w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n    json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"ready\"})\n}\n```\n\n### middleware/logging.go\n\n```go\ntype LoggingMiddleware struct {\n    logger Logger\n}\n\nfunc (m *LoggingMiddleware) Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n    return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n        start := time.Now()\n        \n        ww := &responseWriterWrapper{ResponseWriter: w}\n        next.ServeHTTP(ww, r)\n        \n        m.logger.Info(\"request\",\n            \"method\", r.Method,\n            \"path\", r.URL.Path,\n            \"status\", ww.status,\n            \"duration\", time.Since(start),\n        )\n    })\n}\n```\n\n### middleware/recovery.go\n\n```go\ntype RecoveryMiddleware struct {\n    logger Logger\n}\n\nfunc (m *RecoveryMiddleware) Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n    return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n        defer func() {\n            if err := recover(); err != nil {\n                m.logger.Error(\"panic recovered\", \"error\", err, \"path\", r.URL.Path)\n                http.Error(w, \"Internal Server Error\", http.StatusInternalServerError)\n            }\n        }()\n        next.ServeHTTP(w, r)\n    })\n}\n```\n\n### types.go\n\n```go\ntype ErrorResponse struct {\n    Code    string `json:\"code\"`\n    Message string `json:\"message\"`\n    Details any    `json:\"details,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SuccessResponse struct {\n    Data any `json:\"data\"`\n}\n\nfunc HandleError(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request, err error) {\n    // 根据 error 类型映射到 HTTP 状态码\n    // 统一返回 ErrorResponse JSON\n}\n```\n\n## API Endpoints\n\n### Health Endpoints\n\n| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |\n|----------|--------|---------|\n| `/healthz` | GET | 健康检查（Kubernetes liveness probe） |\n| `/readyz` | GET | 就绪探针（Kubernetes readiness probe） |\n\n### API Group\n\n| Prefix | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `/api/v1` | 业务 API 路由组（待后续 AR 实现） |\n\n### Middleware Chain\n\n```\nRecovery → Logging → CORS (optional) → Business Handler\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n\n| Error Type | HTTP Status | Error Code |\n|------------|-------------|------------|\n| Validation Error | 400 | `VALIDATION_ERROR` |\n| Not Found | 404 | `NOT_FOUND` |\n| Internal Error | 500 | `INTERNAL_ERROR` |\n| Service Unavailable | 503 | `SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE` |\n\n统一错误响应格式:\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n  \"message\": \"Invalid request parameter\",\n  \"details\": {\"field\": \"name\", \"reason\": \"required\"}\n}\n```\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test Category | Coverage |\n|---------------|----------|\n| HTTPServer 启动/关闭 | 测试优雅关闭逻辑 |\n| HealthHandler | 测试 `/healthz` 和 `/readyz` 端点 |\n| Middleware | 测试日志、恢复、CORS 中间件 |\n| 错误处理 | 测试 HandleError 返回正确的 JSON 格式 |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Test | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| 端到端请求 | 启动真实 HTTP 服务器，发送请求并验证响应 |\n| 中间件链 | 验证中间件按预期顺序执行 |\n\n### Test File Structure\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n  server_test.go\n  router_test.go\n  handlers/health_test.go\n  middleware/logging_test.go\n  middleware/recovery_test.go\n```\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n  server.go              — HTTPServer 实现\n  router.go              — Router 封装\n  config.go              — Config 结构体\n  types.go               — 公共类型定义\n  handlers/\n    handler.go           — Handler 接口\n    health.go            — HealthHandler 实现\n  middleware/\n    logging.go           — 日志中间件\n    recovery.go          — Panic 恢复中间件\n    cors.go              — CORS 中间件\n```\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- 是否需要 WebSocket 支持？（暂不在范围内，待后续 AR）\n- 是否需要限流中间件？（暂不在范围内，待后续 AR）\n- 日志库选型：pkg/logging 还是第三方（如 zap、logrus）？\n- 指标端点 `/metrics` 是否在本 AR 范围内？（建议预留路由，实现待后续 AR）\n\n## References\n\n- chi router: https://github.com/go-chi/chi\n- Go net/http: https://pkg.go.dev/net/http\n- Kubernetes API conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md","after":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，提供 RESTful API 基础设施、中间件架构、生命周期管理。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\ncmd/workload-manager/\n    └── main.go                    — 入口，调用 pkg/workloadmanager\npkg/workloadmanager/\n    ├── server.go                  — HTTPServer 核心实现\n    ├── router.go                  — 路由配置与路由组\n    ├── config.go                  — 配置结构体\n    ├── types.go                   — 公共类型定义\n    ├── doc.go                     — 包文档\n    ├── handlers/\n    │   ├── handler.go             — Handler 接口\n    │   └── health.go              — 健康检查实现\n    └── middleware/\n        ├── logging.go             — 请求日志中间件\n        ├── recovery.go            — Panic 恢复中间件\n        └── cors.go                — CORS 中间件\n```\n\n### Kubernetes Client Integration\n\nWorkloadManager 使用 `client-go` 与 Kubernetes API 交互:\n\n| Client | API Group | Resource | Purpose |\n|--------|-----------|----------|---------|\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` | `agentruntimes` | 管理 AgentRuntime CR |\n| `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` | `codeinterpreters` | 管理 CodeInterpreter CR |\n\nClient construction pattern:\n\n```go\nimport (\n    versioned \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n    \"k8s.io/client-go/rest\"\n)\n\nfunc NewKubernetesClient(config *rest.Config) (versioned.Interface, error) {\n    return versioned.NewForConfig(config)\n}\n```\n\nTyped client interfaces:\n\n```go\ntype RuntimeV1alpha1Interface interface {\n    RESTClient() rest.Interface\n    AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface\n    CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterInterface\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeInterface interface {\n    Create(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.CreateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Update(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    UpdateStatus(ctx context.Context, agentRuntime *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, opts metav1.UpdateOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    Delete(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.DeleteOptions) error\n    Get(ctx context.Context, name string, opts metav1.GetOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n    List(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList, error)\n    Watch(ctx context.Context, opts metav1.ListOptions) (watch.Interface, error)\n    Patch(ctx context.Context, name string, pt types.PatchType, data []byte, opts metav1.PatchOptions, subresources ...string) (*runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, error)\n}\n```\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `net/http` | 标准库 HTTP 服务器 |\n| `context` | 请求上下文 |\n| `sync` | 并发控制（优雅关闭） |\n| `os/signal` | 信号处理 |\n| `time` | 超时配置 |\n\n### Router Library Selection\n\n**决策**: 使用 `go-chi/chi` v5\n\n| Aspect | Rationale |\n|--------|-----------|\n| 零外部依赖 | 仅依赖 Go 标准库 |\n| 兼容 net/http | 可使用所有标准库中间件 |\n| 路由分组 | 支持路由组与中间件作用域 |\n| 性能 | 足够优秀（参考 benchmark） |\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### server.go\n\n```go\ntype HTTPServer struct {\n    server   *http.Server\n    router   chi.Router\n    config   Config\n    handlers map[string]Handler\n    logger   Logger\n    stopCh   chan struct{}\n}\n\ntype Config struct {\n    Addr              string        // 监听地址，如 \":8080\"\n    ReadTimeout       time.Duration // 读超时\n    WriteTimeout      time.Duration // 写超时\n    IdleTimeout       time.Duration // 空闲连接超时\n    ShutdownTimeout   time.Duration // 优雅关闭超时\n    EnableHealthz     bool          // 是否启用健康检查\n    EnableReadyz      bool          // 是否启用就绪探针\n}\n```\n\n### router.go\n\n```go\ntype Router struct {\n    chi.Router\n}\n\nfunc NewRouter() *Router {\n    r := chi.NewRouter()\n    return &Router{Router: r}\n}\n\nfunc (r *Router) RegisterHandlers(handlers ...Handler) {\n    for _, h := range handlers {\n        h.Register(r.Router)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### handlers/handler.go\n\n```go\ntype Handler interface {\n    Register(r chi.Router)\n}\n\ntype HandlerFunc func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) error\n\nfunc (hf HandlerFunc) ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n    if err := hf(w, r); err != nil {\n        HandleError(w, r, err)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### handlers/health.go\n\n```go\ntype HealthHandler struct {\n    checker HealthChecker\n}\n\ntype HealthChecker interface {\n    IsHealthy() bool\n    IsReady() bool\n}\n\nfunc (h *HealthHandler) Register(r chi.Router) {\n    r.Get(\"/healthz\", h.healthz)\n    r.Get(\"/readyz\", h.readyz)\n}\n\nfunc (h *HealthHandler) healthz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n    w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n    json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"ok\"})\n}\n\nfunc (h *HealthHandler) readyz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n    if h.checker == nil || !h.checker.IsReady() {\n        w.WriteHeader(http.StatusServiceUnavailable)\n        json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"not ready\"})\n        return\n    }\n    w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n    json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"ready\"})\n}\n```\n\n### middleware/logging.go\n\n```go\ntype LoggingMiddleware struct {\n    logger Logger\n}\n\nfunc (m *LoggingMiddleware) Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n    return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n        start := time.Now()\n        \n        ww := &responseWriterWrapper{ResponseWriter: w}\n        next.ServeHTTP(ww, r)\n        \n        m.logger.Info(\"request\",\n            \"method\", r.Method,\n            \"path\", r.URL.Path,\n            \"status\", ww.status,\n            \"duration\", time.Since(start),\n        )\n    })\n}\n```\n\n### middleware/recovery.go\n\n```go\ntype RecoveryMiddleware struct {\n    logger Logger\n}\n\nfunc (m *RecoveryMiddleware) Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n    return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n        defer func() {\n            if err := recover(); err != nil {\n                m.logger.Error(\"panic recovered\", \"error\", err, \"path\", r.URL.Path)\n                http.Error(w, \"Internal Server Error\", http.StatusInternalServerError)\n            }\n        }()\n        next.ServeHTTP(w, r)\n    })\n}\n```\n\n### types.go\n\n```go\ntype ErrorResponse struct {\n    Code    string `json:\"code\"`\n    Message string `json:\"message\"`\n    Details any    `json:\"details,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SuccessResponse struct {\n    Data any `json:\"data\"`\n}\n\nfunc HandleError(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request, err error) {\n    // 根据 error 类型映射到 HTTP 状态码\n    // 统一返回 ErrorResponse JSON\n}\n```\n\n## API Endpoints\n\n### Health Endpoints\n\n| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |\n|----------|--------|---------|\n| `/healthz` | GET | 健康检查（Kubernetes liveness probe） |\n| `/readyz` | GET | 就绪探针（Kubernetes readiness probe） |\n\n### API Group\n\n| Prefix | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `/api/v1` | 业务 API 路由组（待后续 AR 实现） |\n\n### Middleware Chain\n\n```\nRecovery → Logging → CORS (optional) → Business Handler\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n\n| Error Type | HTTP Status | Error Code |\n|------------|-------------|------------|\n| Validation Error | 400 | `VALIDATION_ERROR` |\n| Not Found | 404 | `NOT_FOUND` |\n| Internal Error | 500 | `INTERNAL_ERROR` |\n| Service Unavailable | 503 | `SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE` |\n\n统一错误响应格式:\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n  \"message\": \"Invalid request parameter\",\n  \"details\": {\"field\": \"name\", \"reason\": \"required\"}\n}\n```\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test Category | Coverage |\n|---------------|----------|\n| HTTPServer 启动/关闭 | 测试优雅关闭逻辑 |\n| HealthHandler | 测试 `/healthz` 和 `/readyz` 端点 |\n| Middleware | 测试日志、恢复、CORS 中间件 |\n| 错误处理 | 测试 HandleError 返回正确的 JSON 格式 |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Test | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| 端到端请求 | 启动真实 HTTP 服务器，发送请求并验证响应 |\n| 中间件链 | 验证中间件按预期顺序执行 |\n\n### Test File Structure\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n  server_test.go\n  router_test.go\n  handlers/health_test.go\n  middleware/logging_test.go\n  middleware/recovery_test.go\n```\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n  server.go              — HTTPServer 实现\n  router.go              — Router 封装\n  config.go              — Config 结构体\n  types.go               — 公共类型定义\n  handlers/\n    handler.go           — Handler 接口\n    health.go            — HealthHandler 实现\n  middleware/\n    logging.go           — 日志中间件\n    recovery.go          — Panic 恢复中间件\n    cors.go              — CORS 中间件\n```\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- 是否需要 WebSocket 支持？（暂不在范围内，待后续 AR）\n- 是否需要限流中间件？（暂不在范围内，待后续 AR）\n- 日志库选型：pkg/logging 还是第三方（如 zap、logrus）？\n- 指标端点 `/metrics` 是否在本 AR 范围内？（建议预留路由，实现待后续 AR）\n\n## References\n\n- chi router: https://github.com/go-chi/chi\n- Go net/http: https://pkg.go.dev/net/http\n- Kubernetes API conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md","additions":44,"deletions":0},"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","time":{"start":1775841923289,"end":1775841923313}}}}
